{"tid":1201490,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"IT狗叫唔好用Telegram","createTime":"2019-06-11T04:56:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T09:40:15.000Z","uid":154277,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d1dac8a94f49017efbe47a8dafbdb59847acd2e9","tid":1201490,"uid":154277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:56:13.000Z","msg":"Telegram 安全備受質疑<br />\n<br />\n坊間多誤以為 Telegram 乃高度保密通訊工具，事實上，其安全性比 WhatsApp 更低！<br />\n<br />\n誠然，2013 年 Telegram 初推出之際，WhatsApp 根本無加密機制，是以當時 Telegram 確是超英趕美，然而今時今日，WhatsApp 早加入強制端對端加密，其安全性自不可同日而語。<br />\n<br />\n關於加密， Telegram 一向備受質疑，首先，其加密算式 MTProto 從未經過密碼專家審核，相反地，WhatsApp、Signal，以及 Wire，皆採用有多位專家背書 [1] 之 Signal 加密協議。<br />\n<br />\n更甚者，Telegram 最近被揭發有嚴重漏洞，原來其對 chat bot 通訊竟有如冇掩雞籠，黑客只需作普通中間人攻擊，即可撮取受害人對 chat bot 歷來所有訊息 [2]！<br />\n<br />\n撇除如此驚人漏洞，Telegram 之根本設計，都係相當耐人尋味。其他工具比如 WhatsApp，強制使用端對端加密，訊息只會存於通訊雙方手機 [3]，而 Telegram 預設加密模式卻並非端對端，訊息自動上載雲端伺服器，不知受何方監察（除非特別開通 &ldquo;secret chat&rdquo; 頻道，而群組通訊則根本不支援端對端加密）。<br />\n<br />\n更匪夷所思者，Telegram 本月初更新，竟自動公開使用者電話號碼予通訊錄上有資料者，切切實實是保安降級 [4]！本研究所認為此行為完全不負責任。<br />\n<br />\n基於以上原因，若要安全，如常使用 WhatsApp 就好，iPhone 版本更佳。<br />\n<br />\n註:<br />\n[1] <a href=\"https://threatpost.com/signal-audit-reveals-protocol-cryptographically-sound/121892/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthreatpost.com%2Fsignal-audit-reveals-protocol-cryptographically-sound%2F121892%2F&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVDzizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=93441d0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://threatpost.com/signal-audit-reveals-protocol-cryptographically-sound/121892/</a><br />\n[2] <a href=\"https://www.wired.com/story/telegram-bots-tls-encryption/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2Fstory%2Ftelegram-bots-tls-encryption%2F&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVDzizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=bf8aff03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wired.com/story/telegram-bots-tls-encryption/</a><br />\n[3] <a href=\"https://www.whatsapp.com/security/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fsecurity%2F&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVDzizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=5c43c3e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.whatsapp.com/security/</a><br />\n[4] <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ericfankm.hk/posts/2315019992052295\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fericfankm.hk%2Fposts%2F2315019992052295&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVDzizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=a8a2d8d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ericfankm.hk/posts/2315019992052295</a><br />\n<br />\n伸延閱讀:<br />\n[5] <a href=\"https://www.csoonline.com/article/3273344/what-is-telegram-and-is-it-secure.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.csoonline.com%2Farticle%2F3273344%2Fwhat-is-telegram-and-is-it-secure.html&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVDzizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=5bbd1b5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.csoonline.com/article/3273344/what-is-telegram-and-is-it-secure.html</a><br />\n<br />\nSource: 9hack Labs Facebook"},{"pid":"958e19ef437c94d5022175bcf4ad00bacf37a5dc","tid":1201490,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:57:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ef87dcff0d4ef2197d7bd4deba0af1498d9c6e5","tid":1201490,"uid":154277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:05:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"edb4d34284d9146f740d957ac57e9d8fd1389133","tid":1201490,"uid":154277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:08:47.000Z","msg":"Telegram 安全備受質疑<br />\n<br />\n坊間多誤以為 Telegram 乃高度保密通訊工具，事實上，其安全性比 WhatsApp 更低！<br />\n<br />\n誠然，2013 年 Telegram 初推出之際，WhatsApp 根本無加密機制，是以當時 Telegram 確是超英趕美，然而今時今日，WhatsApp 早加入強制端對端加密，其安全性自不可同日而語。<br />\n<br />\n關於加密， Telegram 一向備受質疑，首先，其加密算式 MTProto 從未經過密碼專家審核，相反地，WhatsApp、Signal，以及 Wire，皆採用有多位專家背書 [1] 之 Signal 加密協議。<br />\n<br />\n更甚者，Telegram 最近被揭發有嚴重漏洞，原來其對 chat bot 通訊竟有如冇掩雞籠，黑客只需作普通中間人攻擊，即可撮取受害人對 chat bot 歷來所有訊息 [2]！<br />\n<br />\n撇除如此驚人漏洞，Telegram 之根本設計，都係相當耐人尋味。其他工具比如 WhatsApp，強制使用端對端加密，訊息只會存於通訊雙方手機 [3]，而 Telegram 預設加密模式卻並非端對端，訊息自動上載雲端伺服器，不知受何方監察（除非特別開通 &ldquo;secret chat&rdquo; 頻道，而群組通訊則根本不支援端對端加密）。<br />\n<br />\n更匪夷所思者，Telegram 本月初更新，竟自動公開使用者電話號碼予通訊錄上有資料者，切切實實是保安降級 [4]！本研究所認為此行為完全不負責任。<br />\n<strong><br />\n基於以上原因，若要安全，如常使用 WhatsApp 就好，iPhone 版本更佳。更進一步，若不希望公開電話號碼，可使用 Wire（<a href=\"https://wire.com/en/download/）。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwire.com%2Fen%2Fdownload%2F%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVDzizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=62287286\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://wire.com/en/download/）。</a></strong><br />\n<br />\n註:<br />\n[1] <a href=\"https://threatpost.com/signal-audit-reveals-protocol-cryptographically-sound/121892/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthreatpost.com%2Fsignal-audit-reveals-protocol-cryptographically-sound%2F121892%2F&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVDzizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=93441d0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://threatpost.com/signal-audit-reveals-protocol-cryptographically-sound/121892/</a><br />\n[2] <a href=\"https://www.wired.com/story/telegram-bots-tls-encryption/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2Fstory%2Ftelegram-bots-tls-encryption%2F&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVDzizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=bf8aff03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wired.com/story/telegram-bots-tls-encryption/</a><br />\n[3] <a href=\"https://www.whatsapp.com/security/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fsecurity%2F&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVDzizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=5c43c3e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.whatsapp.com/security/</a><br />\n[4] <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ericfankm.hk/posts/2315019992052295\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fericfankm.hk%2Fposts%2F2315019992052295&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVDzizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=a8a2d8d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ericfankm.hk/posts/2315019992052295</a><br />\n<br />\n伸延閱讀:<br />\n[5] <a href=\"https://www.csoonline.com/article/3273344/what-is-telegram-and-is-it-secure.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.csoonline.com%2Farticle%2F3273344%2Fwhat-is-telegram-and-is-it-secure.html&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVDzizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=5bbd1b5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.csoonline.com/article/3273344/what-is-telegram-and-is-it-secure.html</a>"},{"pid":"68ea773a1c8a038613fe8f135f5aaf0be1fbc162","tid":1201490,"uid":154277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:09:22.000Z","msg":"更新：可轉用Wire"},{"pid":"27c0dc0043b661f45a0b2f099c80fc2d77177d95","tid":1201490,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:10:25.000Z","msg":"俄佬嘢都好信 嗰陣啲人吹捧得幾勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79877284e77b7652e6c0672eb215e46e96012d8b","tid":1201490,"uid":154277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:15:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">PUSH</span>"},{"pid":"fcddebd6b05c33bdf53fa34ccb9421b322d3dc3f","tid":1201490,"uid":154277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:22:26.000Z","msg":"有冇人推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01a61813a9b3f9d1d0eb40ebadf2f4ae8eff87bb","tid":1201490,"uid":99607,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:23:59.000Z","msg":"用乜撚野都一樣"},{"pid":"c6fb79ddd9203f9620f5b7b4d9f0bcc32d00a9ad","tid":1201490,"uid":145277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68ea773a1c8a038613fe8f135f5aaf0be1fbc162","tid":1201490,"uid":154277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:09:22.000Z","msg":"更新：可轉